Package: simlite
Type: Package
Title: Simulation functions for sequencing count matrices based on common distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mukai Wang
Maintainer: Mukai Wang <wangmk@umich.edu>
Description: This package can be used to simulate high throughput sequencing counts based on common parametric distributions.
    The distributions include Poisson, gamma, negative binomial and log normal distribution. Zero inflation can be introduced.
    The user can also specify dependence structure between covariates with Gaussian copulas.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
